dsOverview.title: USGS Selected 3-Second Elevations for Colorado, Hawaii, and the U.S. Great Plains

summary.p: This dataset contains 3-second terrain elevation data, from the U.S. Geological Survey, for Colorado, Hawaii, and the U.S. Great Plains covered by the Storm Fest project.
